<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٠٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1580">الْحَكَمِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/128">إِبْرَاهِيمَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4490">عَلْقَمَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3913">عَبْدِ اللهِ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«صَلَّى النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> الظُّهْرَ خَمْسًا،<span class="c5"> فَقَالُوا:</span> أَزِيدَ فِي الصَّلَاةِ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَمَا ذَاكَ؟.<span class="c5"> قَالُوا:</span> صَلَّيْتَ خَمْسًا،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٩٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَثَنَى رِجْلَيْهِ، وَسَجَدَ سَجْدَتَيْنِ».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>